data.description: Garden Level Condo in Waterford Park with easy access to freeways, employment, and shopping.  This well cared for home features 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, high-efficiency triple-pane windows, and a functional floorplan.  The two covered, designated parking spaces are close by, and the clubhouse has a pool. Outside there is a private patio surrounded by mature trees and lush landscaping. Upgraded blinds and shades add privacy while still allowing in natural light.  This charming condo shows beautifully - make your appointment today!  This is a probate sale, and as such, will be an as-is sale - the estate will not complete repairs. Contact listing agent for Attorney and Escrow information.
